clashes between
I.S. fighters and the Iraqi
security forces.

31:24.916 --> 31:30.088 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Susannah, you
alluded to this
earlier, but these new bombings
in Baghdad

31:30.121 --> 31:37.028 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
