territory.

32:17.001 --> 32:21.572 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right,
Susannah George
of the AP in Baghdad, thank you
very much.

32:21.606 --> 32:29.180 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
SUSANNAH GEORGE: Thank you.

32:29.213 --> 32:36.454 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: One of the great
medical advances
in recent years is the treatment
and care

32:36.487 --> 32:38.756 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of premature babies.

32:38.790 --> 32:44.729 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
