born before
full term are still at higher
risk for a range

32:44.762 --> 32:46.898 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
of problems down the road.

32:46.931 --> 32:51.936 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Correspondent William Brangham
and producer
Jason Kane bring us the first of
two stories

32:51.970 --> 32:57.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about a study under way that's
