here in Morgan Stanley
Children's hospital,

33:38.216 --> 33:39.183 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for months.

33:39.217 --> 33:42.720 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN: OK, now we're going to go
