need, so I can

37:03.454 --> 37:05.356 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
bring them home.

37:05.389 --> 37:09.894 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Her twin boys,
Lukas (ph)
and Tadeo (ph), were born at 26
weeks, three-and-a-half

37:09.927 --> 37:11.929 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
months too soon.

37:11.963 --> 37:18.069 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
