not.

37:59.377 --> 38:01.846 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I really didn't want to get
close with
them.

38:01.879 --> 38:05.016 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I didn't want to -- I don't
know.

38:05.049 --> 38:06.951 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's hard to describe that
feeling.

38:06.984 --> 38:11.255 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Like everyone
who was part
of this intervention, Cardenas
was also encouraged

38:11.289 --> 38:15.660 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to talk with the boys, and
