38:22.333 --> 38:24.468 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
pressure she can use on the
boys.

38:24.502 --> 38:25.703 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

38:25.736 --> 38:29.473 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTHA WELCH: I was trying to
elicit emotion
from Elia.

38:29.507 --> 38:35.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
