what she's doing to the baby.

38:46.791 --> 38:48.793 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ELIA CARDENAS: I'm trying to be
here for them.

38:48.826 --> 38:49.794 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

38:49.827 --> 38:50.795 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARTHA WELCH: And you have been.

38:50.828 --> 38:51.796 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ELIA CARDENAS: Yes.

38:51.829 --> 38:52.797 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
