38:57.668 --> 38:59.737 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ELIA CARDENAS: No, it doesn't.

38:59.770 --> 39:00.738 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

39:00.771 --> 39:01.839 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MARTHA WELCH: It will.

39:01.872 --> 39:03.774 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
