make her feel like that, the
baby's viable.

39:14.985 --> 39:17.088 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MIGUELINA TAVAREZ, Mother: We
had eggs.

39:17.121 --> 39:19.690 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
After dinner, I told my dad a
ghost story.

39:19.724 --> 39:21.625 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Boy, did he get scared.

39:21.659 --> 39:26.197 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Another mother
in the study,
Miguelina Tavarez, says she
can't really explain

39:26.230 --> 39:31.302 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
