interventions have had
a powerful effect or her ability
to connect

39:31.335 --> 39:33.003 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
with her daughter Reylan (ph).

39:33.037 --> 39:37.708 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIGUELINA TAVAREZ: I actually
come in now,
and I can take a deep breath and
be like,

39:37.742 --> 39:38.709 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I'm all right.

39:38.743 --> 39:40.544 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And she's all right.

39:40.578 --> 39:42.847 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then, in the long run, I
will be like,
you know what, me and you have a
trust besides

39:42.880 --> 39:48.119 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a mother and a daughter bond,
that I can express
myself to you, and you will
appreciate it.

39:48.152 --> 39:52.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Today, she's
learning another
part of the intervention: using
what's known

39:52.423 --> 39:53.391 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
as a scent cloth.

39:53.424 --> 39:55.226 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

39:55.259 --> 39:58.195 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTHA WELCH: We have a little
flannel square
that the mother wears in her
bra, which she

39:58.229 --> 39:59.997 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
then gives to the baby.

40:00.030 --> 40:04.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we put the same kind of
cloth under the
baby's head, and give that to
the mother.

40:04.835 --> 40:08.439 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MIGUELINA TAVAREZ: I felt like
my whole body
was relaxed.

40:08.472 --> 40:09.640 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

40:09.673 --> 40:10.441 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTHA WELCH: How do you feel
now when you
smell it?

40:10.474 --> 40:11.442 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MIGUELINA TAVAREZ: The same way.

40:11.475 --> 40:12.443 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's like...

40:12.476 --> 40:13.444 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

40:13.477 --> 40:15.146 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARTHA WELCH: Let all the stress
drain out.

40:15.179 --> 40:19.116 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But do these
interventions
