higher performance
in students overall.

52:43.994 --> 52:49.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So when you show that kind of
data, you're
seeing a higher percentage of
students really

52:49.232 --> 52:52.669 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
showing strong academic
performance where
there is high arts investments.

52:52.702 --> 52:57.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The next step,
McDade says,
is to measure the impact of the
poetry classes.

52:57.707 --> 53:02.612 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The district has signed on for
another year
and will track the effectiveness
of the program

53:02.646 --> 53:04.214 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
for both teachers and their
students.

53:04.247 --> 53:11.421 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUAN FELIPE HERRERA: Dinky
planet on a skateboard
of dynamite, oh, what to do?

53:11.454 --> 53:16.593 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: As for Juan
Felipe Herrera,
his term as U.S. poet laureate
is ending,

53:16.626 --> 53:20.163 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
